ong>Levels:<\/strong> Bachelor\u2019s, Master\u2019s and PhD<\/li><li><strong>Study Location:<\/strong> The US<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/developers.google.com\/womentechmakers\">Official Website<\/a><\/li><\/ul><p>Women Techmakers Scholars Program provides scholarships for women from Africa (as well as Europe and the Middle East) to study computer science, computer engineering, or a closely related technical field at any study level.<\/p><p>The program encourages women to become Ambassadors, providing opportunities to lead, network, learn, and shine. Additionally, members can empower other women by organizing events and offering access to resources.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><h2>9. The Beit Trust Scholarships for African Students<\/h2><ul><li><strong>Levels:<\/strong> Master\u2019s and PhD<\/li><li><strong>Study Locations:<\/strong> The UK, Ireland, or South Africa<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/beittrust.org.uk\/beit-trust-scholarships\/\">Official Website<\/a><\/li><\/ul><p>International master\u2019s degree and PhD scholarships for African students from Malawi, Zambia, or Zimbabwe to study in the UK, Ireland, or South Africa at a leading university.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><h2>10. Oppenheimer Fund Scholarships<\/h2><ul><li><strong>Levels:<\/strong> Master\u2019s and PhD<\/li><li><strong>Study Location:<\/strong> The UK<\/li><li><a href=\"http:\/\/www.ox.ac.uk\/admissions\/graduate\/fees-and-funding\/fees-funding-and-scholarship-search\/scholarships-2#oppenheimer\">Official Website<\/a><\/li><\/ul><p>Oppenheimer Fund Scholarships are for Africans who have previously studied at South African universities to study in the UK at Oxford University. Students should be applying to study a full-time master\u2019s or DPhil course.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><h2>11. Edinburgh African Scholarships<\/h2><ul><li><strong>Levels:<\/strong> Master\u2019s and PhD<\/li><li><strong>Study Location:<\/strong> Scotland<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.napier.ac.uk\/study-with-us\/bursaries\">Official Website<\/a><\/li><\/ul><p>The University of Edinburgh offers some merit-based graduate scholarships to study in this university in Scotland on a master\u2019s or PhD program.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><h2>12. Ruth First Scholarships<\/h2><ul><li><strong>Levels:<\/strong> Master\u2019s and PhD<\/li><li><strong>Study Location:<\/strong> The UK<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ruthfirsttrust.webspace.durham.ac.uk\/\">Official Website<\/a><\/li><\/ul><p>These are scholarships for Africans from Angola, Botswana, Lesotho, Malawi, Mozambique, Namibia, South Africa, Zambia, and Zimbabwe to undertake postgraduate study in the UK at Durham University.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><h2>13. Zawadi Africa Education Fund<\/h2><ul><li><strong>Level:<\/strong> Bachelor\u2019s<\/li><li><strong>Study Locations:<\/strong> The US, Uganda, Ghana, South Africa and Kenya<\/li><li><a href=\"http:\/\/www.zawadiafrica.org\/\">Official Website<\/a><\/li><\/ul><p>Zawadi Africa Education Fund provides female students from disadvantaged backgrounds from Africa some scholarships to study in other African countries or the US.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><h2>14. Wells Mountain Foundation Scholarships for African Students<\/h2><ul><li><strong>Level:<\/strong> Bachelor\u2019s<\/li><li><strong>Study Locations:<\/strong> Worldwide<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wellsmountaininitiative.org\/prospective-scholars\/\">Official Website<\/a><\/li><\/ul><p>Wells Mountain Foundation scholarships are needs-based grants for students from African nations to gain funding for university at home or in a country in the developing world.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><h2>15. Mandela Rhodes Scholarships<\/h2><ul><li><strong>Levels:<\/strong> Master\u2019s and PhD<\/li><li><strong>Study Location:<\/strong> South Africa<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.mandelarhodes.org\/scholarship\/apply\/\">Official Website<\/a><\/li><\/ul><p>These scholarships are for Africans with strong leadership skills to study for an honors or master\u2019s degree at a recognized university in South Africa.<\/p><p>if you want to know about <a href=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/phd-scholarships-in-germany\/\">PhD scholarships in Germany<\/a> read this article:<\/p><p><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"dci2hosti8\"><a href=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/phd-scholarships-in-germany\/\">Top 10 PhD Scholarships in Germany for 2024-2025<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden;\" title=\"&#8220;Top 10 PhD Scholarships in Germany for 2024-2025&#8221; &#8212; Abroadin \" src=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/phd-scholarships-in-germany\/embed\/#?secret=Cv54qvPMRy#?secret=dci2hosti8\" data-secret=\"dci2hosti8\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/p><p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2652 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/study-group-african-people-1-scaled.webp\" alt=\"scholarships for african students\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/study-group-african-people-1-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/study-group-african-people-1-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/study-group-african-people-1-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/study-group-african-people-1-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/study-group-african-people-1-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/study-group-african-people-1-2048x1365.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/p><h2>16. 7UP Harvard Business School Scholarships<\/h2><ul><li><strong>Level:<\/strong> Master\u2019s<\/li><li><strong>Study Location:<\/strong> The 